%F A004255 a(n) = A062026(n)/2.
%F A004255 G.f.: -x*(1-2*x+4*x^2)/(x-1)^5. - _Simon Plouffe_ in his 1992 dissertation.
%F A004255 a(n) = Sum_{i=0..n} (i(i-2)^2 + i^2)/2.
%F A004255 a(n) = binomial(n+3,4) - 2*binomial(n+2,4) + 4*binomial(n+1,4).
%F A004255 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, Sep 09 2025: (Start)
%F A004255 E.g.f.: exp(x)*x*(x^3 + 4*x^2 + 4*x + 8)/8.
%F A004255 a(n) = 5*a(n-1) - 10*a(n-2) + 10*a(n-3) - 5*a(n-4) + a(n-5) for n > 5. (End)
%F A004255 Sum_{n>=1} (-1)^(n+1)/a(n) = 32*log(2)/15 - 11/15 + 4*Pi*sech(sqrt(15)*Pi/2)/15. - _Amiram Eldar_, Nov 01 2025
